OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1775394665
OL,3,CTwo men arrested after man dies in
OL,4,Ccollision near Atherstone
OL,6,FTwo men have been arrested after a
OL,7,Fman's body was discovered in a road
OL,8,Fnear Atherstone in the early hours of
OL,9,FFriday morning.
OL,11,FThe body of the man in his 50's was
OL,12,Fdiscovered in Monk's Park Lane just
OL,13,Fafter 1.30am.
OL,15,FPolice say they understand at this
OL,16,Fstage that a vehicle collided with the
OL,17,Fman and left the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
