OL,3,CTwo men arrested after man dies in
OL,4,Ccollision near Atherstone
OL,6,FPC Craig Pearson from Warwickshire
OL,7,FPolice's Serious Collision
OL,8,FInvestigation Unit said: "An
OL,9,Finvestigation into the incident has
OL,10,Fstarted to establish the circumstances
OL,11,Fsurrounding this tragic incident.
OL,13,F"I'm especially keen to speak to
OL,14,Fanyone who saw or has video footage of
OL,15,Fa red Mercedes Vito van in the area
OL,16,Faround the time of the incident. I'd
OL,17,Fask anyone in the area to please check
OL,18,FCCTV, doorbell cameras and dashcam
OL,19,Ffootage.
